content.description:
Second route on the tower, first from the bottom of the tower.

1-st pitch 100' 5.10 corner to sandy/loose crux C1 (5.11 on TR) to ledges; possible class 2-4 traverse to right;

2-nd pitch 110' OW 5.10 and easy chimney to ledge;

3-rd pitch 50' overhang start C1 (for cleaning, possible 5.11) to grove/chimney/bowl to loose rock below the summit;
